  <body>
    <div class="content">

      <h1>SpacialDB API</h1>

      <hr/>

      <h2>SpacialDB Management API</h2>
      <div id="introduction">
      <p>
        The goal of the <strong>SpacialDB Management API</strong> is two fold.
        Firstly for managing your <strong>geospatial database</strong> by performing the following operations on your database via a RESTful API:
        <ul>
          <li>creating</li>
          <li>listing</li>
          <li>deleting</li>
        </ul>

        Secondly for managing your <strong>user account</strong> by performing the following operations via a RESTful API:
        <ul>
          <li>sign up</li>
          <li>login</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
      </div>

      <h2>Resources</h2>
      <div id="resources">
        <ul>
        <% @resources.each do |r| %>
          <li>Resource:  <a href="/apidoc/<%=r.name %>.html"><%=r.resource_location %></a></li>
        <% end %>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>
